    "- id: ULID text, primary key",
    "- transactionId: TransactionFact.id, RESTRICT",
    "- eventType: enum {voided,superseded}",
    "- replacementTransactionId: TransactionFact.id, nullable, required only for superseded",
    "- reason: text, required",
    "- occurredAt: trusted UTC instant",
    "- actorContext: attributable metadata",
    "category_allocation",
    "- id: ULID text, primary key",
    "- transactionId: TransactionFact.id, RESTRICT",
    "- categoryId: SpendCategory.id, RESTRICT",
    "- state: enum {active,retired}",
    "- replacesAllocationId: nullable self reference",
    "- reason: text, required for correction",
    "- createdAt/retiredAt and actorContext",
    "Constraints: one terminal transaction lifecycle; one active allocation per active transaction; corrections append and retire atomically; supersession does not migrate relationships."
